            </svg> 
           </picture> <h4 class="h-c-headline h-c-headline--four highlights-module__subhead">Tailor your measurement with Ads Data Hub.</h4> <p class="highlights-module__description">Use Ads Data Hub to join event-level campaign data from Google Marketing Platform and Google Ads with data from your own sources, such as a CRM system or marketing database, to run customized analysis that aligns to your specific business objectives while protecting user privacy.</p> <p> <a data-g-event="for enterprises" data-g-action="ads data hub" data-g-label="learn more" href="https://developers.google.com/ads-data-hub" title="Learn More" class="h-c-link h-c-link--internal gmp-link" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noreferrer noopener">Learn More</a></p> </li> 
